15:21.454 --> 15:22.789
know?

15:22.889 --> 15:25.125
Does that mean
you're swingers, too, now?

15:25.225 --> 15:28.861
No. We enjoy hanging out
with Connie and Ted,

15:28.962 --> 15:31.698
but we made it clear
that very first night

15:31.798 --> 15:33.833
