Quite to the contrary.

16:09.902 --> 16:10.870
(gasps)

16:10.970 --> 16:13.040
People come here to swing.

16:13.140 --> 16:14.407
And swing.

16:14.507 --> 16:16.409
Our. Parents.

16:16.509 --> 16:18.411
