the message, hun.

19:05.978 --> 19:10.082
(British accent) Now your
worst fear will come true!

19:10.183 --> 19:12.419
(laughs)

19:12.519 --> 19:14.053
This is the same guy
that bit my finger

19:14.153 --> 19:16.022
